==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dapifer
<hw>Dap"i*fer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.,
<ets>daps</ets> a feast + <ets>ferre</ets> to bear.]</ety> <def>One who
brings meat to the table; hence, in some countries, the official title
of the grand master or steward of the king's or a nobleman's
household.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dapper</ent>⟦br⟧
